---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="AI Prompt Sheet for Trades Businesses | Crystal AI"
  description="13 ready-to-use AI prompts for HVAC, plumbing, and electrical contractors. Follow-ups, estimates, customer communication, and operations. Print it and start using it today."
>

  <section class="band">
    <div class="frame lp">
      <p class="eyebrow">FREE PROMPT SHEET</p>
      <h1>13 AI Prompts for Trades Businesses</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">Ready-to-use instructions for ChatGPT, Claude, or any AI chat. Print it. Tape it to your desk. Start using it today.</p>

      <a href="/downloads/follow-up-prompt-sheet.pdf" class="cta-btn" download>Download the Prompt Sheet (PDF)</a>

      <div class="card">
        <p class="card-label">WHAT'S ON THE SHEET</p>
        <div class="prompt-grid">
          <div class="prompt-group">
            <p class="group-label">Follow-Up System</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Day-3 check-in</li>
              <li>Week-2 nudge</li>
              <li>Last-chance before quote expires</li>
              <li>Post-job review ask</li>
              <li>Referral tap</li>
              <li>Past customer re-engage</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="prompt-group">
            <p class="group-label">Estimates & Communication</p>
            <ul>
              <li>Messy notes to clean estimate</li>
              <li>Scope of work write-up</li>
              <li>Reply to a complaint</li>
              <li>Quick reply to a new lead</li>
              <li>Overdue invoice follow-up</li>
              <li>Crew job instructions</li>
              <li>Google review response</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="card-note">Plus 3 blank slots to add your own prompts as you find what works.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <p class="card-label">HOW TO USE IT</p>
        <ol class="steps">
          <li>Fill out the Business Brief from the <a href="/playbook">Playbook</a> (5 minutes, one time)</li>
          <li>Open any AI chat and paste your Brief</li>
          <li>Copy a prompt from the sheet, fill in the brackets, hit send</li>
        </ol>
      </div>

      <div class="companion">
        <p>Haven't set up your Business Brief yet? Grab the <a href="/playbook">Playbook</a> first — it walks you through the whole system in 10 minutes.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="cta-footer">
        <a href="/downloads/follow-up-prompt-sheet.pdf" class="cta-btn" download>Download the Prompt Sheet (PDF)</a>
        <p class="fine-print">No email required. Just the prompts.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</Base>

<style>
  .band {
    padding: 4rem 0;
  }

  .lp {
    max-width: 620px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .eyebrow {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .subtitle {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
  }

  .cta-btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.9rem 2rem;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: background 150ms ease;
  }

  .cta-btn:hover {
    background: var(--accent-hover);
  }

  .card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 2rem;
    text-align: left;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .card-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .card-note {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    margin: 1rem 0 0;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .prompt-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 520px) {
    .prompt-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }

  .group-label {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--ink);
    margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
  }

  .prompt-group ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .prompt-group li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--ink-2);
    line-height: 1.45;
  }

  .prompt-group li::before {
    content: '—';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .steps {
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .steps li {
    margin-bottom: 0.65rem;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--ink-2);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .steps li:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .steps a {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .steps a:hover {
    color: var(--accent-hover);
  }

  .companion {
    margin-top: 2rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 1.5rem;
    background: var(--paper-2);
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  .companion p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--ink-2);
  }

  .companion a {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .companion a:hover {
    color: var(--accent-hover);
  }

  .cta-footer {
    margin-top: 2.5rem;
  }

  .fine-print {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--ink-muted);
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }
</style>
